&lt;li&gt;Collaborate in high-impact projects from beginning to end, working with autonomy and accountability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively engage in problem-solving, fault-finding, and addressing issues in the data or approaches as they arise.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Read research papers and develop/build concepts/ideas into Prototypes or Proof of Concepts (POC).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, build, and orchestrate complex AI workflows using Agentic frameworks like LangGraph.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop advanced knowledge retrieval pipelines, including building, evaluating, and optimizing GraphRAG and semantic search systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experiment with advanced prompt/context engineering techniques and fine-tune open-source Large Language Models (LLMs) using parameter-efficient techniques (e.g., LoRA, QLoRA) for domain-specific tasks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement robust evaluation frameworks (e.g., LLM-as-a-judge, RAGAS, DeepEval) to monitor and ensure the quality, safety, and relevance of Generative AI outputs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communication (visual, verbal, and written) of findings to a variety of audiences, including colleagues and clients, both technical and non-technical.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Bring to Us:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Degree or advanced training in statistics, mathematics, computer science, or other highly quantitative field or 2-4 years of work experience related to the field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of advanced statistical and analytical techniques and concepts such as sampling methods, regression, properties of distributions, weighting sample-based data, statistical tests and proper usage, etc. and experience with real-world applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of data structures, databases, and ETL processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Applied Machine Learning and Deep Learning experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with production ML deployments, including containerization, cloud computing environments, modern data warehousing, workflow orchestration, and infrastructure-as-code.&lt;/li&gt;
