&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;13,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;13,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Market Competitive Advantage:&lt;/strong&gt; Guide the strategic direction of identity solutions to further expand Innovid’s market differentiation in video measurement, ensuring resilience against ecosystem deprecations (e.g., cookies, device IDs).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
